                            ],
                            Label: "workbench_button"
                        },
                        {
                            Name: "Back to Bo Huan",
                            Actions: [
                                {
                                    Type: "OPEN_DEFAULT_DIALOG"
                                }
                            ],
                            Label: "back_button"
                        },
                        {
                            Name: "Goodbye",
                            Actions: [
                                {
                                    Type: "CLOSE_DIALOG"
                                }
                            ],
                            Label: "goodbye_button"
                        }
                    ],
                    Texts: [
                        {
                            Text: "Two to a bundle, one hundred twenty the pair. Pick a color. The black jar sits on the workbench shelf with the tumblestones — ask if you do not see it."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "The hill decides the colors, not me. Warm rows lean one morning, cool rows the next — what I foraged at dawn is what hangs on the cart. The basket on the workbench never argues, if you cannot wait."
                        }
                    ],
                    Name: "Bo Huan — the seven colors",
                    Label: "colors"
                },
                {
                    Priority: -1,
                    Buttons: [
                        {
                            Name: "Black Apricorns x2 — 120 CD",
